<p>Welcome! We are committed to protecting your privacy and want you to be aware of what information we collect, why we collect it, and how we use it. This Privacy Policy describes our practices regarding the collection, processing, and sharing of your personal data.</p>

<h2>What information do we collect?</h2>

<p>While using our site, we may collect various types of information, including:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Personal Information: such as your name, email address, and phone number, voluntarily provided by you, for example, during registration or when placing an order.</li>
    <li>Automatic Information: such as IP address, browser details, language preferences, device data, and information about your activity on the site.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Why do we collect this information?</h2>

<p>We collect your information for the following purposes:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Providing services and delivering products that you order.</li>
    <li>Customizing and improving our website.</li>
    <li>Conducting analyses and statistics related to the use of our site.</li>
    <li>Ensuring the security and protection of our website.</li>
</ul>

<h2>How do we use your information?</h2>

<p>Your personal information is used only for the purposes for which it was collected. We do not share it with third parties without your consent, except when necessary for providing services (e.g., payment processors) or as required by applicable laws.</p>

<h2>How do we protect your information?</h2>

<p>We implement technical and organizational measures to ensure the security of your information, preventing unauthorized access, loss, alteration, or destruction.</p>

<h2>Your rights</h2>

<p>You have the right to access, correct, delete, or restrict the processing of your personal data. You can also withdraw any previously given consent for processing. Contact us to exercise these rights.</p>

<h2>Changes to the Privacy Policy</h2>

<p>This Privacy Policy may be subject to change. All updates will be posted on this page, and the last update date will be revised accordingly.</p>

